name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: We have the cast of "Game of Thrones" tonight. I went to see them in the green room. They're all dead.

name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: The cast of "The Walking Dead" is also here. They were in the green room. They're eating the bodies of the cast of "Game of Thrones."

name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: The new "Star Wars" movie was directed by J.J. Abrams. "Star Wars" fans were very excited until they realized that J.J. stands for Jar Jar.

name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: Comic-Con is a hot bed for romantic action. Yesterday I was checking out San Diego's Craigslist personals. The categories were men seeking women, women seeking men, and Marvel seeking D.C.
